all the invasions of history have been determined by petticoats
romulus carried off the sabines william carried off the saxon women caesar carried off the roman women
the man who is not loved so are like a culture over the mistresses of other men and for my own part to all those unfortunate men who are widowers i throw the sublime proclamation of bonaparte to the army of italy soldiers you are in need of everything the enemy has it
