do you know what aspasia was ladies
although she lived at an epoch when women had as yet no soil she was a soul a soul of a rosy and purple hue more ardent nude than fire greater than the dawn
aspasia was a creature in whom two extremes of womanhood net she was the goddess prostitute socrates plus manon lescaut
