t holon yes once started would have found some difficulty in stopping had not a horse fallen down upon the quay just at that moment
the shock caused the cart and the orator to come to a dead halt
it was a beauceron made old and thin and onefit for the knacker which was dragging a very heavy cart
this incident attracted a crowd
hardly had the cursing and indignant carter had time tougher with proper energy the sacramental word marin they are backed up with a pitiless cut of the ship when they are fell never to rise again
