i will explain it to you you see you are earning twelve sousa t shirt making the price falls to nine sold and it is not enough to live on
then one has to become whatever one can
as for me i had my little cosette and i was actually forced to become a bad woman
now you understand how it is that that blackguard of a major causes all the mischief
we women have but one silk dress for evening wear
you see that i did not do wrong deliberately truly monsieur have grand everywhere i behold women who are far more wicked than i and who are much happier
