fantine laid her head on her pillow and said on a low voice yes lie down again be good for you are going to have your child sisters implode is right everyone here is right
and then without stirring without even moving her head she began to share all about her with wide open eyes and a joyous air and she said nothing more
the sister drew the curtains together again hoping that she would fall into a dose
