the doctor recommended silence and that all painful emotions should be avoided be prescribed an infusion of pure chin china and in case the fever should increase again during the night a calming potion
as he took his departure he said to the sisters he is doing better in good luck willed that the mayor should actually arrive tomorrow with the child who knows
there are crises do astounding great joy has been known to arrest maladies i know well that this is an organic disease and in an advanced state but all those things are such mysteries we may be able to save her
the landlady of the hotel entered
