she explained to him what had passed that fantine had been very ill the day before and that she was better now because she thought that the mayor had gone to mont vermeil together child
the sister dared not question the mayor but she perceived plainly from his air that he had not come from there
all that is good said he you were right not to undeceive her
yes responded the sister but now mr
mayor she will see you and will not see her child
what shall we say to her
