the police had supposed that he had be taken himself to paris
paris is a karla from where everything is lost and everything disappears in this belly of the world as in the belly of the sea
no forest hides a man as does that crowd
fugitives of every sort know this
they go to paris as to an abyss there are rules which save
the police know it also and it is in paris that they seek what they have lost elsewhere
they sought the ex mayor of m
