he had screen his bouquet there
at the extremity of the grave on a little swelling which marked the head there stood a cross of black wood with this name in white letters colonel baron pont mercy
the laws was a grave
chapter viii marble against granite it was higher that marius had come on the first occasion of his absenting himself from paris
