all civilized peoples offer this detail to the admiration of the thinker war now war civil ized war exhausts and sums up all the forms of ruffian i am from the brigandage of the tragic eros in the gorges of month as a to the marauding of the comanche indians in the doubtful pass
gentlemen of the human race i tell you not a bit of it
it is at brussels that the most beer is consumed at stockholm the most brandy at madrid the most chocolate at amsterdam the most fun at london the most wine at constantinople the most coffee at pad is the most absinthe there are all the useful notions
