well sir my worthy sir do you know what is going to happen tomorrow
tomorrow is the fourth day of february the fatal day the last day of grace allowed me by my landlord if by this evening i have not paid my tent tomorrow my oldest daughter my spouse with her fever my child with her wound we shall all four be turned out of here and thrown onto the street on the boulevard without shelter in the rain in the snow
